{"tid":1071091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［好撚迫］屌你老母，香港根本就唔夠地方去容納更多人","createTime":"2019-03-21T06:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T07:32:20.000Z","uid":15933,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b42294d2d64cf7bebc9caf45ea6b99e4411bd14a","tid":1071091,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:12:27.000Z","msg":"你老母個臭西 返工迫 食飯迫 放工繼續迫  落街買個飯都好多人 周圍都好多人 想唞啖氣都唞唔到 你老母死狗官垃撚圾 日撚日放一百件落嚟 包容包容 包你老母垃圾閪呀 咁撚大方唔好讓埋你間屋企比啲蝗住？<br />\n<br />\n地方就得咁多，日日放人入嚟迫走香港人，搶資源搶福利，睇醫生排期排到下年，又入嚟霸學位，屋都霸撚埋，比撚埋個骨灰龕你好唔撚好呀？ 知唔知點解你地大陸人去到邊都咁黑人憎呀？搶人啲嘢聲大夾惡，仲要比你班生番踩多兩腳，然後抬高自己偉大嘅祖國，咁撚好你死返大陸啦，出嚟做咩姐？托柒呀？嗱，屎呀，食唔食呀？搶唔搶呀賤人<br />\n<br />\n利申：啱啱比人迫完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚嬲"},{"pid":"8cea9c7bd3cbbcc1095ec9a3371933e331575e1f","tid":1071091,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲 推到有人一齊入嚟屌柒班垃圾"},{"pid":"8b7f1a95081c473526f11ceee0a26504bc4110c9","tid":1071091,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"仲有你班垃圾大財團呀，車你都夠膽反撚埋，游水返工o唔ok呀"},{"pid":"9cad0935eff7fe758d84a20705cc34376470231d","tid":1071091,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"cb6c23ded4c0d6a7b78e288e81c8241b0a8ca584","tid":1071091,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"出曬面賣港嘅狗官政府我都係第一次見 手指拗出唔坳入 有冇良心呀你班垃圾？"},{"pid